#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:2
msgid "Breakout rooms"
msgstr "Seomraí scoite amach"

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:4
msgid ""
"Breakout rooms allow you to divide a Nextcloud Talk call into smaller groups"
" for more focused discussions. The moderator of the call can create multiple"
" breakout rooms and assign participants to each room."
msgstr ""
"Le seomraí scoite, is féidir leat glao Nextcloud Talk a roinnt ina ghrúpaí "
"níos lú le haghaidh plé níos dírithe. Is féidir le modhnóir an ghlao seomraí"
" scoite iolracha a chruthú agus rannpháirtithe a shannadh do gach seomra."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:6
msgid ""
"Breakout rooms are currently not available in conversations that are "
"joinable by guests (public conversations)."
msgstr ""
"Níl seomraí scoite ar fáil faoi láthair i gcomhráite ar féidir le haíonna "
"páirt a ghlacadh iontu (comhráite poiblí)."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:9
msgid "Configure breakout rooms"
msgstr "Cumraigh seomraí scoite amach"

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:11
msgid ""
"To create breakout rooms, you need to be a moderator in a group "
"conversation. Click on the top-bar menu and click on ``Setup breakout "
"rooms``."
msgstr ""
"Chun seomraí scoite amach a chruthú, ní mór duit a bheith i do mhodhnóir i "
"gcomhrá grúpa. Cliceáil ar an roghchlár sa bharra uachtarach agus cliceáil "
"ar ``Socraigh seomraí scoite amach``."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:16
msgid ""
"A dialog will open where you can specify the number of rooms you want to "
"create and the participants assignment method. You have three options:"
msgstr ""
"Osclófar bosca dialóige inar féidir leat líon na seomraí is mian leat a "
"chruthú agus an modh sannta rannpháirtithe a shonrú. Tá trí rogha agat:"

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:19
msgid ""
"**Automatically assign participants**: Talk will automatically assign "
"participants to the rooms."
msgstr ""
"**Sannadh rannpháirtithe go huathoibríoch**: Sannfaidh Talk rannpháirtithe "
"do na seomraí go huathoibríoch."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Manually assign participants**: You'll go through a participants editor "
"where you can assign participants to rooms."
msgstr ""
"**Sannadh rannpháirtithe de láimh**: Rachaidh tú trí eagarthóir "
"rannpháirtithe inar féidir leat rannpháirtithe a shannadh do sheomraí."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Allow participants choose**: Participants will be able to join breakout "
"rooms themselves."
msgstr ""
"**Lig do rannpháirtithe rogha a dhéanamh**: Beidh rannpháirtithe in ann "
"páirt a ghlacadh i seomraí scoite iad féin."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:27
msgid "Manage breakout rooms"
msgstr "Bainistigh seomraí scoite amach"

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:29
msgid ""
"Once the breakout rooms are created, you will be able to see them in the "
"sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh na seomraí scoite cruthaithe, beidh tú in ann iad a fheiceáil"
" sa bharra taoibh."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:34
msgid "From the sidebar header, you can:"
msgstr "Ó cheanntásc an bharra taoibh, is féidir leat:"

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Start and stop the breakout rooms**: this will move all the users in the "
"parent conversation to their respective breakout rooms."
msgstr ""
"**Tosaigh agus stop na seomraí scoite**: bogfaidh sé seo na húsáideoirí go "
"léir sa chomhrá tuismitheora chuig a seomraí scoite faoi seach."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Broadcast a message to all the rooms**: this will send a message to all "
"the rooms at the same time."
msgstr ""
"**Craol teachtaireacht chuig na seomraí uile**: seolfar teachtaireacht chuig"
" na seomraí uile ag an am céanna leis seo."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Make changes to the assigned participants**: this will open the "
"participants editor where you can change which participants are assigned to "
"which breakout room. From this dialog it's also possible to delete the "
"breakout rooms."
msgstr ""
"**Déan athruithe ar na rannpháirtithe sannta**: osclóidh sé seo eagarthóir "
"na rannpháirtithe inar féidir leat athrú a dhéanamh ar na rannpháirtithe atá"
" sannta do sheomra scoite ar leith. Ón dialóg seo is féidir na seomraí "
"scoite a scriosadh freisin."

#: ../../talk/breakout_rooms.rst:43
msgid ""
"From the breakout room element in the sidebar, you can also join a "
"particular breakout room or send a message to a specific room."
msgstr ""
"Ón eilimint seomra scoite amach sa bharra taoibh, is féidir leat dul isteach"
" i seomra scoite amach ar leith nó teachtaireacht a sheoladh chuig seomra ar"
" leith freisin."
